	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Jul 5th 4:18 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here it is, my very first post ever!&nbsp;&nbsp;I am fairly new to the game (been playing around a month) and play on Vallon Zek.  My first instinct was to make a wizzy.  Unfortunatly, after 3 weeks of endless death and turmoil i had only reached lev 9 while all my other friends had easily surpassed me to the point I dont get exp from grouping with them any more.  Frustrated, I tried both an enchanter and a necro and was able to lev to 9 in like 2 days.  I really love my wizzy and would love to find a way to make her a little more efficient.  If any of you could give me advice I would appreciate it.  I am a dark elf and have spent the vast majority of my time in Nektulos forest, with trips to Lavastorm and East Commons being disasters.  Sorry about the long winded post here.  Any help would be appreciated.<br><br>"The fate of all light-walkers will be tempered in destruction and forged on the anvil of Innoruuk's hatred"<br>(new but feelin that racial pride)<br>~~Kagaro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
